es, are extinct.  See also  Rupert ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When Robert de Stavelegh II was born about 1230, in Northamptonshire, England, United Kingdom, his father, Robert de Stavelegh I, was 27 and his mother, Dionisia MacClesfeld, was 25. He married Margaret de Worslegh. They were the parents of at least 1 son."},"et":{"about 1230–Deceased":"umbes 1230–Surnud","1230–Male":"1230–Surnud","1232–Male":"1232–Surnud","1234–Male":"1234–Surnud","1232–Female":"1232–Surnud","1255–Male":"1255–Surnud","1205–Male":"1205–Surnud","1207–Female":"1207–Surnud","1205":"1205","1234":"1234","1255":"1255","1232":"1232","1230":"1230","about 1230":"umbes 1230","1207":"1207","Northamptonshire, England":"Northamptonshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"about 1230–Deceased":"noin 1230–Kuollut","1230–Male":"1230–Kuollut","1232–Male":"1232–Kuollut","1234–Male":"1234–Kuollut","1232–Female":"1232–Kuollut","1255–Male":"1255–Kuollut","1205–Male":"1205–Kuollut","1207–Female":"1207–Kuollut","1205":"1205","1234":"1234","1255":"1255","1232":"1232","1230":"1230","about 1230":"noin 1230","1207":"1207","Northamptonshire, England":"Northamptonshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"about 1230–Deceased":"environ 1230–Décédé","1230–Male":"1230–Décédé","1232–Male":"1232–Décédé","1234–Male":"1234–Décédé","1232–Female":"1232–Décédée","1255–Male":"1255–Décédé","1205–Male":"1205–Décédé","1207–Female":"1207–Décédée","1205":"1205","1234":"1234","1255":"1255","1232":"1232","1230":"1230","about 1230":"environ 1230","1207":"1207","Northamptonshire, England":"Northamptonshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Lorsque Robert de Stavelegh II est né environ 1230, à Northamptonshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, son père, Robert de Stavelegh I, avait 27 ans et sa mère, Dionisia MacClesfeld, avait 25 ans. Il a épousé Margaret de Worslegh. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fils."},"de":{"about 1230–Deceased":"um 1230–Verstorben","1230–Male":"1230–Verstorben","1232–Male":"1232–Verstorben","1234–Male":"1234